How to reach Grand Royal St. Kitts by Taxi

Finding your way from port to Grand Royal St. Kitts is easy when you have a car. You will reach the destination in about 9 minutes if you take Cab, and the overall cost of your trip will be INR 958.

This in inclusive of the trip to the destination and the return trip back, which can be easily fixed using Free Cancellation option available in most packages. Free cancellation benefits save you from the costs of cancellation, in case the tour is cancelled due to unfavorable weather.

How to reach Grand Royal St. Kitts by Water Taxi

Water Taxi is another popular transportation option for Navigate to Grand Royal St. Kitts. From the port you have to reach to Ham. Tobako Bay and the travel from there to Grand Royal St. Kitts will take you 38 minutes by Water Taxi. The rate starts at INR 3808.

How to reach Grand Royal St. Kitts by Public Bus

Another way of going to Grand Royal St. Kitts is to take a public bus. The bus takes about 62 minutes to get you there. The cost for this trip is about INR 912.
